        <div class="divtitle">
            What's a Project ?</div>
        <div class="divmatter" align="left">
            <div class="divleftother">
                <p class="matter" style="width: 305px; padding-left: 30px; font-size: 14px; text-align: left;
                    line-height: 20px;">
                    <span class="spanbig">A project </span>is a scheme for setting up a manufacturing
                    or infrastructure facility or expanding capacity of an existing facility or modernizing
                    an old one.
                </p>
                <p class="matter" style="width: 305px; padding-left: 30px; font-size: 14px; text-align: left;
                    line-height: 20px;">
                    <span class="spanbig">The promoter </span>- ultimate owner of the project - drafts
                    a scheme for setting up a manufacturing facility for certain product or infrastructure
                    project such as airport, seaport or hotel, hospital.
                </p>
                <p class="matter" style="width: 305px; padding-left: 30px; font-size: 14px; text-align: left;
                    line-height: 20px;">
                    The promoter appoints a <span class="spanbig">technical consultant </span>for engineering
                    services such as technology or product knowhow, designing process, short listing
                    vendors/contractors, site supervision, etc. Based on recommendations of the consultant,
                    contract for construction of the plant is awarded to a contractor.
                </p>
                <p class="matter" style="width: 305px; padding-left: 30px; font-size: 14px; text-align: left;
                    line-height: 20px;">
                    <span class="spanbig">These contractors </span>procure equipment from the manufacturers
                    approved by the consultant and construct the facility at site.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="divrightother">
                <img alt="What is Projects?" src="images/capexbdcssimages/What'saProject.png" height="420px"
                    style="padding-top: 30px;" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
